Require the concerned Accountable Officers to submit the accounts and financial reports to the Municipal Treasurer on or before the fifth day after the end of the month, who should, thereafter, submit the same to the Accounting Office for recording and transmittal to the Auditor pursuant to the abovementioned pertinent provisions of law, rules and regulations, as applicable;

